{"tid":1894188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有副校長俾人搞","createTime":"2020-02-23T18:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T19:02:08.000Z","uid":92188,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"276ddd4cc2a62064a52f6308d9ae9ac80bc35bac","tid":1894188,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:14:19.000Z","msg":"孔聖堂中學校董會聲明<br />\n<br />\n就有關署理副校長何栢欣老師近日在網上針對警方貼文一事，本校董會作出以下聲明：<br />\n<br />\n1. 何副校長是以個人名義在其個人Facebook專頁發表該文。該文章與本校無關，而該篇貼文發表事前未曾知會本會，亦未尋求本會的許可，屬於其個人行為。<br />\n<br />\n2. 孔聖堂中學及其校董會一直堅守政治中立，反對暴力及任何違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n3. 本校董會已成立了專責調查小組，務求查明該事件的來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n4. 於2月24日起，何副校長將暫時停職，直至調查小組完成報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1484748651847035/posts/2584151945240028/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1484748651847035%2Fposts%2F2584151945240028%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=0cbe225d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1484748651847035/posts/2584151945240028/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"f0ebfa6d3f82a4ce11a521d1cde49b0fb5aa28bb","tid":1894188,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:16:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a32b926ed26344d320695ce056c5871827c300f8","tid":1894188,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"(武肺文宣戰) 點解應上網扮支那人出盡奶力批鬥人地支援得武漢唔夠力&amp;道德綁架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4281ab9cecc3c2c0b607874809849956c8b8dc94","tid":1894188,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0e5c5a6f8c3d2a83c8c1a40dcb7414a153dcb84","tid":1894188,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"［黃色新聞圈］香港人 肯 撐 良 心 傳 媒 未，肯唔好扼殺佢地未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893867\" data-auto-li